summary: An ordinance appropriating money from Local Improvement District No. 1346 Fund, to be paid the owner of lot 1 and lot 2, block 4, Bigelow's Addition to the City of Seattle, as a refund of assessment for the construction of a sewer, under Ordinance No. 14994. Creating Local Improvement District No. 1346, and appropriating money from the general fund to be paid into said Local Improvement District No. 1346 Fund, to make up the deficiency in said district fund hereby created.
